{"tid":1671989,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】人人都係岑子杰，自己遊行自己申請","createTime":"2019-10-24T00:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T01:11:55.000Z","uid":252840,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92139b917a38339a3c257c33ae7bb967ed7aa9a3","tid":1671989,"uid":252840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:06:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">d和理飛成日遊行都要人地幫你申請，有埋不反對通知書先岀黎。其實按公安條例，只要無反對通知書，就當係不反對。</span><br />\n<br />\n按《公安條例》，如警務處處長針對集會或是遊行，可以對提出遊行及集合意圖的組織者，發出不反對通知書（Letter of No Objection）[1][2]。然而<strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\">假如處長在指定期限內沒有發出不反對通知書，只要處長沒有發出反對遊行的通知，仍可視為已發出不反對通知書。</span></strong>唯若警方發出反對通知書，則代表遊行被禁止。雖然如此，警方無論有沒有發出不反對通知書，若參加遊行，仍可能會被視為非法集結[3]。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">次次都搵民陣申請遊行，有無諗過人人都可以係民陣？自己遊行自己申請！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果超過一萬人都申請同一日遊行，佢係咪全部都可以發反對通知書？？？</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">萬人申請百萬遊行，還香港人和平示威既權利！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點申請：<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/rights/givenotice/givenotice.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fgovernment%2Frights%2Fgivenotice%2Fgivenotice.htm&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yEV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=25137b94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/government/rights/givenotice/givenotice.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nps. p牌post請幫推"},{"pid":"4e534233d5b1b86300cf68987125ade7b6dafb7a","tid":1671989,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T00:07:07.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[堅行動post]三分鐘Twitter 戰線傳送門 10月24號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671967</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fed6df59b1052e8802361d0faeca604505531723","tid":1671989,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1